Caption: Figure 1. SeeBill interactively displays a four-dimensional mul- tiway table. The hierarchical choropleth map uses color and size to encode values, under the control of the double-thumb slid- ers to the left. The four buttons below the map allow the user to select any combinations of the direction and endpoint dimen- sions. Histograms in separate windows are used to display and select on the region and time-of- day dimensions.
